snippet.title: Official Trailer – Ikémen Prince: Beauty and Her Prince (Otome Game)
snippet.description:
You've been selected as "Belle" to choose the next king out of eight princes. If that wasn't hard enough, the princes turn out to be hot...and deadly. They're not rumored to be beasts for no reason. 


In a world of war and intrigue, will you be able to save his heart and yours as you enter your very own fairy tale?


Enjoy a gorgeous game with an all-star cast!
Leon Dompteur (Voice: Kazuki Kato)
Chevalier Michel (Voice: Yuki Ono)
Yves Kloss (Voice: Uchida Yuma)
Nokto Klein (Voice: Takuya Eguchi)
Licht Klein (Voice: Shoichiro Oomi)
Clavis Lelouch (Voice: Kenji Nojima)
Jin Grandet (Voice: Hiroki Yasumoto)
Luke Randolph (Voice: Sion Yoshitaka)
Sariel Noir (Voice: Show Hayami)

Rio Ortiz (Voice: Hiromu Mineta)


Check out the official twitter for more information, in-game campaigns and special giveaways!


https://twitter.com/ikepri_en


#ikemenseries #otome #cybird
